	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Sounds great.  The only difficulty on the hardware side is the fact that the original SID chip had analog components.  This creates unique distortion effects that can't quite seem to be matched digitally.  That's part of what makes the SID so pleasing on original hardware.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


